    section#price.price.bg-primary.text-center
      .container
        .row
          .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
            h2.section-heading Best price in Squamish
            p.text-muted
              | This table compares the price of our locally roasted nuts and organic fruit against the cheapest (not organic) available similar product at these popular Squamish grocers. Prices are per pound as of 6/10/2017.
